Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnarok
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do we have to wait here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not earning anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The prince got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were right about Wessex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the short end of the stick--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's another one! \N-Get away! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never go to Valhalla at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a bunch of scarecrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Damn that bastard! \N-He's so full of himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you has any balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting him insult us like this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is a disgrace to us warriors! Let's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 4000 men. I'm sure we can beat Thorkell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. We're talking about Thorkell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't make a careless move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness put us in charge of the siege.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance to distinguish ourselves \Nas warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, \NHis Highness shall give the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the Lord was told,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Put your sword back into its place,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for all those who take up the sword \Nshall perish by the sword."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father. Excuse me. Can you leave us alone \Nfor a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Orders? Who cares! \N-The prince is a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to sit here silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When winter comes, \Nwe will receive the order to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to endure until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,God, please protect His Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! What's wrong with you? You guys are no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hard at work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they being mean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Asgeir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have a battle if they don't attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so loud. I bet they're just being more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're under the command of the Prince of Denmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is the Prince here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The second prince, His Highness Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And my sister too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ari is slacking off again watching the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the other day, they were saying that \None went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's time for dinner! \NI have to go tell Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having meat tonight. \NWe're celebrating Yule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? It's already the winter solstice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty warm, so I had forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's enough grass for the animals. \NI'm glad we moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister says it's inconvenient living here \Nbecause we can't get any slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never even had a slave, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother seems to be feeling better after we moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my oldest son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to protect your mother and your sister. \NYou understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both waiting for you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Having people like that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is a happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So stop thinking about revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that would make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! What are we going to do? We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with rolling plains of grass...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as the eye can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,NOVEMBER, 1013 \NOUTSKIRTS OF BATH
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is our leader thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The main army withdrew to the north \Na long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're still here picking off \Ngloomy villages like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have to earn what we can \Nbefore going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should attack a bigger city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bristol is near here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do with only 100 men?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just call me stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, you heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess your ears aren't stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all that's left for this year \Nis to plunder two or three more villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope next year's going to be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll still have a chance \Nnext year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been plundering England \Nfor ten years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This year was especially horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the King of England \Nescaped overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That means \Nthat the King of Denmark has won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The war is coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I think it's still too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell's in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw how strong he is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell, huh? He is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's Norse, just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the English are about to die, \Nhe'd ditch them in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him, Tore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Why are they fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ake called Tore stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tore got mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ake wouldn't apologize \Nand insulted him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Cattle thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you tell Askeladd afterwards, \Nno matter who dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A fertile land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the land I saw in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really different from Iceland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the snow is beginning \Nto pile up around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up early, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun hasn't even come up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you couldn't sleep \Nbecause they're too loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, go easy on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They were frustrated since we've been \Nmarching a lot these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to relax sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me like we're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you think you have me \Nunder your control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're full of yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll stop when I slit \Nyour throat someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you fall over and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined that little kid would glare \Nat me someday. You've grown a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, time is on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to grow, \Nand I'm going to get old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I'm going to lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the strongest dies someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around you, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These stones weren't made by the people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,who live in England now, the Saxons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They were made by the people who lived here \Nbefore the Saxons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they were a strong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But they were destroyed \Nby the Saxons 500 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were the Romans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of their country was Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They had an advanced civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,More advanced than what we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You should listen to what your elders say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the world of man
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is getting older gradually, but surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Saxons destroyed the Romans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to destroy the Saxons next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The glory of the Roman Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is a thing of the distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, according to what \Nthe Christians are saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the Last Judgment is coming \Nin only 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, God will kill everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and our world will be completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnarok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ironic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dawn in the age of twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an English soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He's an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird. \NI thought we were the only ones in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Askeladd's unit, under King Sweyn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you from the main army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Ragnar's unit \Nunder His Highness Prince Canute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-I've got a message for the main force! \N-Prince Canute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they close by?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the main army is far north.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on their way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just trying to earn some pocket money \Nin that village over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You separated from the army on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your horse looks tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to trade it for a new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's 500 men. He took along only \Nhis immediate followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're following the main army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to reach Marlborough soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-They're so close! \N-Attacking the main army with only 500?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the unit laying siege to London?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Prince Canute had 4000 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They were defeated a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of the survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With Thorkell leading them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,they came out of the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all as strong as bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making a beeline for the main army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness! Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, may they rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-I pray that their souls may be saved-- \N-Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell is close! \NWe must leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what happened to His Highness Canute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They captured him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's with Thorkell's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining soldiers are trying to regroup \Nto go get His Highness back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have less than 400 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And their morale is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to ask the main army for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Join us. We'd be grateful to have \Neven 100 extra men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do? It's your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. This isn't the time for us \Nto just fade into the twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear it, Bjorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of Ragnarok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bury him. And the horse he was riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go save \NHis Highness Prince Canute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up against 500 of Thorkell's men! \NBut we're not going to ask for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to place our bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness Canute is second in line
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for the throne of Denmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get a lot of money no matter \Nwhich side we hand him over to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the rewards we'd be granted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by the rulers of Denmark and England?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let someone else take it away from \Nright under our noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it! This is going to be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do \Nnow that you've stirred them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up against Thorkell. \NDo you have a plan for winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who knows"? Are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the age of twilight, Bjorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あー…ったく冷えやがるな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつまでここでにらめっこしてんだぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,稼ぎになんねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子が怖気づいてんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:39.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こりゃあウェセックスがあたりだったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:40.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違えねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:44.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく、貧乏くじ引いち…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:55.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,りゃああああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,またくるぞ！\Nさがれ！さがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:05.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オラーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:08.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とっととかかってこい！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:11.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなんじゃヴァルハラに行けねぇぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:14.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこで突っ立ってるだけか！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:17.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てめぇらカカシかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:20.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそ！あの野郎！\Nもう我慢ならねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:25.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てめぇら！そろいもそろって！タマなしかぁ～～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このまま侮辱を見過ごせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵士としての名折れ！突撃しましょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,皆、士気は充分です！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:41.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我ら4千、必ずやトルケルを討ち取ります！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:46.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだだ…相手はあのトルケル。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うかつに手は出せん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:51.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陛下じきじきに包囲軍を任されたのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:54.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今こそ武勲をあげる機会では…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならん！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:59.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,時が来れば殿下が命を下す。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今は耐えるのだ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル殿…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこで主は彼に言われたのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたの剣をおさめなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:20.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,剣をとる者は皆、剣で滅びるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:26.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神父。すまんが少し外してくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:34.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,命令が何だってんだ！\N腰ヌケ王子が！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつまでも黙ってられるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おお！やろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご心配いりませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,冬になれば撤退命令がなされるはず。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それまでのご辛抱です…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神よ…どうか殿下をお守り下さい…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそっ！なんだよっつまんねー奴らだな！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大将も精が出るなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まーた嫌がらせか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うっせ！アスゲート！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっちが攻めてこねぇと戦になんねぇだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:19.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でけぇよ声が。まあ慎重になってんだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:23.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんせあっちの大将はデンマークの王子様だしな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なに？王子来てんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？言ってなかったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確か第2王子のクヌート殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉上も
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,またアーレたちが羊の番をサボっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:56.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この間も1頭いなくなったって大騒ぎしてたくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:03.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、そーだ晩ゴハンだ。父上を呼びにいかなくっちゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:22.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今晩はお肉だよ！ユルのお祝いだからね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:26.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あーそうか。もう冬至かぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずいぶん暖かいから忘れてたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここはいい所だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,牧草にも不自由しない。移り住んで正解だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:45.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉上は“ここじゃ奴隷が手に入らないから不便だ”\Nって言ってるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴隷買ったことないのにねウチ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつらしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ボクはここ好き。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここに来てから母上も調子いいみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は長男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:13.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上や姉上を守ってやらなきゃだめだぞ。わかるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,2人ともお前の帰りを待ちわびている。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな人がいてくれるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とても幸せなことなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:41.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからな。もう復讐なんてやめろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなことオレが喜ぶと思うのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村が！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:09.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上どうしよう！襲われてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上！姉上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上ーッ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの国じゃ…なかったな…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,暖かくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,草原が波打って…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこまでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しっかし、なに考えてんだろうな。\Nウチの親分は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう冬になるぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本隊はとっくに北に引きあげちまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だのにオレらだけ居残ってこんなシケた村つまんでる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:22.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、少しでもこづかい稼いで帰ろうってことなんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だったらもっとデカい町襲おうぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,近くにブリストルとかあんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,100人ばかしで何ができるってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ？バカ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今バカっつったかオイ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お？聞こえたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,耳だけはバカじゃねーみてーだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだとテメェ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:44.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んだコラァ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:53.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ今年はあと2、3コ村を食って終わりだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また来年に期待しようや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あるかね？来年が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレたちゃもう10年もイングランドを荒らし回ってんだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,特に今年はすさまじかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランド王も国外に逃げたっていうじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:16.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうこりゃデンマーク王の勝ちだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦は終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:22.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうかァ？まだ早いんじゃねーの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:25.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ロンドンにゃあのトルケルがいるぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,野郎のウソくせぇ強さは見ただろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:32.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケルねぇ…確かに強ェけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そもそもありゃオレらと同じノルド人だぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:40.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死に体のイングランドをいつ見限ってもおかしくねェ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あーあー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,またか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オラァーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,コラコラコラ。理由はなんだ理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アークがトーレに“バカ”って言った。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トーレが怒ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アークは謝罪しねェで逆に侮辱した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:04.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんて？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,牛泥棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あーあ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それ言っちゃったかー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んじゃ仕方ねェ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:18.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どっちが死んでもあとでちゃんとアシェラッドに報告しとけよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:19.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,めんどくせぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,豊かな土地だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夢に出てきた土地に似てる…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アイスランドとはえらい違いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:56.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと今頃は雪が積もり始めているだろうな…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:26.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早起きだな。トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ陽も上ってねェぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつらが騒がしくて眠れないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:51.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、カンベンしてやれや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:54.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここんとこ行軍ばかりであいつらもイラついてたからなァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たまにゃああして気晴らしせんと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気やすく話しかけんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,テメェら最近勘違いしてんじゃねぇのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレァテメェらの仲間じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:12.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,テメェはオレをうまいこと操ってるつもりだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今はそうやってうぬぼれてろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレにノドを裂かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くたばるその日までな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怖いね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:29.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのチビガキがオレにガンとばすとは成長したもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:36.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、時間は若いお前の味方だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は成長しオレは老いる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつかお前に負ける日も来るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,当然のことだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どんな強者もいずれは死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:53.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,周りを見てみろトルフィン。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:56.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この石くれは今のイングランドの住人、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,サクソン人が造ったものじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:03.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,サクソンよりも前の住人のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強い民族だったそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:11.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが500年前サクソンに滅ぼされた。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ローマ人だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,国の名は“ブリタニア”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,高度な文明だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今よりもずっとな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,回りくどいんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何が言いてぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せっかちだねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,年寄りの話は聞くもんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まあつまりだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人間の世界はゆるやかに、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:46.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが確実に老いてきてるってことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ローマ人をサクソンが滅ぼし、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:52.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのサクソンを今度はオレたちが滅ぼす。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:58.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのサクソンを今度はオレたちが滅ぼす。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遠い過去になる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:07.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでもキリスト教徒どもの言うことにゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:12.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あと20年もしたら“最後の審判”\Nとやらが下るそうじゃねェか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:22.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その日、人間はすべて神に殺され
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今の世は完全に滅ぶんだそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナロク…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見ろトルフィン。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっけいじゃねェか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:44.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たそがれの時代の夜明けだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,馬だ。1騎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランドの兵か？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:11.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや。ありゃあ友軍だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:17.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,妙だな。ここらにゃオレらしかいないはずだが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:20.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おォい！待たれよ貴公！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我らはスヴェン王配下アシェラッド隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴公はいずれより参られたか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おお！貴公は本隊所属か！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我はクヌート王子殿下のラグナル隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本隊へ伝令に行く途次だ！\Nクヌート王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この近くなのか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいにくだが本隊はずっと北だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう本拠地へ帰りつつある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なら貴公はこんな所で何を？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なにちょいと、そこの村で小銭稼ぎをね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,勝手に部隊から離れたのか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:59.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まあまあカタいこと言うなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,馬も疲れてるようだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんなら新しいのと取り替えてやろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な！トルケルが！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ。もうそこまで来てる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,数は500ほど。奴の直参だけ連れてきたようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本隊の足跡をたどってきてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうじきマールバラに至るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいマジかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,500で本隊とやり合う気か？\Nバカなのか？トルケルって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ロンドンの包囲軍は？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート王子の4千がいたはずだが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなものとっくに撃破されたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:40.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレがその生き残りだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴らトルケルを先頭に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦から打って出てきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:24.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うおらああぁぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:29.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どいつもこいつも熊みてぇに強かった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰もなすすべなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本隊まで一直線だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下…殿下…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,主よ。彼らに安らかな眠りを。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その魂が…\N殿下！殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケルめがそこまで！すぐにここを！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子様みーっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:14.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それで？クヌート殿下はどうなった？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴らのとりこだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケル軍と共にいらっしゃる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:23.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下を奪還すべく残存兵力が再結集を試みているが…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,集まった兵は400に満たない…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,士気も高いとは言えん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:32.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これから本隊へ応援を頼みに行くところだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,。貴公らも加わってくれ。今は100人でもありがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうする？決めるのはあんただ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:47.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:59.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく…おちおちたそがれてもいられねェな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞こえねェかビョルン？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナロクの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:13.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,足音がよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,埋めとけ。こいつの乗ってきた馬もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:42.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっ…あーあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:47.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいかァ野郎ども！よく聞け！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:51.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々は今からクヌート王子殿下の救出に向かう！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:56.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,相手はトルケル以下500！だが他の部隊の手は借りん！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:59.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここがバクチの打ちどころだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート殿下はデンマーク王位継承権
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,第2位のお方！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:07.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どちらの軍に渡しても報酬はたんまりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前ら想像できるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デンマークとイングランド、
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:18.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,2大国の覇者が賜るごほうびを。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:21.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みすみす他の奴らに譲る手はねェぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:24.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おお…おお…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:27.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よぉしやろう！オレたちの手柄だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:29.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やってやろうぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:41.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どーすんだよ。たきつけちまって…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:45.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,相手はトルケルだぞ？勝算あんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:46.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:50.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁなって。お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たそがれの時代だぜビョルン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:58.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうせならブァーッと暴れてみようじゃねェか
